OL,3,C'Extremely weak' porpoise rescued
OL,4,Cafter being found stranded
OL,6,FAn "extremely weak" stranded porpoise
OL,7,Fwas rescued in Guernsey after it was
OL,8,Ffound repeatedly trying to swim to
OL,9,Fshore.
OL,11,FThe porpoise was discovered in poor
OL,12,Fcondition near Vale Castle on Sunday
OL,13,F15 March.
OL,15,FAn islander reported the marine
OL,16,Fcreature to the Guernsey Society for
OL,17,Fthe Prevention of Cruelty to Animals
OL,18,F(GSPCA), but despite their best
OL,19,Fefforts to gently guide and refloat
OL,20,Fthe animal, it showed no desire to
OL,21,Fhead in the right direction to sea.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
