FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1773691869
OL,3,C'Extremely weak' porpoise rescued
OL,4,Cafter being found stranded
OL,6,FThe GSPCA said the animal continued to
OL,7,Fcircle back towards shallow water, and
OL,8,Fa vet was called to the scene shortly
OL,9,Fafter.
OL,11,FWith tide conditions turning against
OL,12,Fthe porpoise's favour, the group
OL,13,Fdecided to move the struggling animal
OL,14,Fto a bathing pool where it could be
OL,15,Fmonitored overnight.
OL,17,FThe porpoise was assessed again on
OL,18,FMonday morning and showed enough
OL,19,Fstrength to be refloated in open water.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
