FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1773691869
OL,3,C'Extremely weak' porpoise rescued
OL,4,Cafter being found stranded
OL,6,FGeoff George, Head of Marine Animals
OL,7,Fat the GSPCA, assisted the animal
OL,8,Fafter its discovery.
OL,10,F"It was a difficult situation, and
OL,11,Fsadly, the porpoise was in a very
OL,12,Fcompromised state when we first
OL,13,Farrived," George said.
OL,15,F"We did everything we could to
OL,16,Fstabilise it, refloat it, and give it
OL,17,Fthe best possible chance with
OL,18,Fveterinary support."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
