FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1773691869
OL,3,C'Extremely weak' porpoise rescued
OL,4,Cafter being found stranded
OL,6,FThe GSPCA have urged Guernsey
OL,7,Fresidents to report any sightings of
OL,8,Fthe animal, in case it takes a turn
OL,9,Ffor the worse.
OL,11,FSteve Byrne, GSPCA Manager, explained:
OL,12,F"Strandings like this are rare but
OL,13,Fincredibly emotional and demanding for
OL,14,Feveryone involved.
OL,16,F"The last stranded sea mammal we
OL,17,Fhelped was 'Fortune' some years ago,
OL,18,Fso we know how important rapid
OL,19,Fresponse and community awareness are
OL,20,Fin these situations.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
