PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1773691869
OL,3,C'Extremely weak' porpoise rescued
OL,4,Cafter being found stranded
OL,6,F"If anyone ever sees a dolphin,
OL,7,Fporpoise, seal, or any marine animal
OL,8,Fin distress, please call the GSPCA
OL,9,Fstraight away.
OL,11,F"The sooner we know, the better the
OL,12,Fchances of helping them."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
